data.description: Come check out this Beaumont beauty tucked in the heart of the West End! Upon arrival, a simplified front landscape welcomes you up to the front entry. This home's fresh updates bring so much charm! The beautiful windows in both dining and living areas allow the home to display so much gorgeous natural light! Into the kitchen, you will find beautifully crafted cabinets, perfect for storing all your culinary necessities! The open view from the kitchen to the sitting area invites guests to gather while you whip up your favorite recipe. Enjoy the gorgeous brick fireplace on those cooler nights when staying home is the perfect cozy space! Out back, the fenced-in backyard is ideal for summer entertainment. Don't let this one pass you by - schedule your showing today!
